  "date": "Tue, 8 Feb 2022 16:45:00 +0000",
  "snippet": "Dear HR Team, I hope this email finds you well. My name is Linda Davis, and I am reaching out on behalf of Professional References to follow up regarding a reference check request for John Smith. Mr.",
  "body": "Dear HR Team,\n\nI hope this email finds you well. My name is Linda Davis, and I am reaching out on behalf of Professional References to follow up regarding a reference check request for John Smith. Mr. Smith has recently applied for a position at one of our client companies, and he has listed your organization as his current employer.\n\nWe kindly request your assistance in verifying some details about Mr. Smith’s employment, which will be used to finalize his application process. These details include:\n\n- Job title\n- Employment dates\n- Core responsibilities\n- Any notable contributions or achievements during his tenure\n\nIf possible, we would also appreciate any insights you are able to provide regarding his work ethic, reliability, and overall performance. Please know that any information shared will be treated with strict confidentiality and used solely for the purpose of this reference check.\n\nYou can respond directly to this email or, if you prefer, call us at (555) 123-4567. Please let us know if there are specific procedures or forms required by your company in order to process this request.\n\nWe appreciate your time and assistance with this matter. If you have any questions or require further details, feel free to reach out.\n\nThank you in advance for your cooperation.\n\nBest regards,  \nLinda Davis  \nProfessional References Team  \nref.check@professionalreferences.com  \n(555) 123-4567\n"
}","annotations":null}

